Configure a python environment
mkdir ransomware && cd ransomware
python3 -m venv env
source env/bin/activate

Simple tool that will encrypt all the files in a directory.
To encrypt all the files run:
python3 encrypt.py
It generates a key using fernet library from python that encrypts the file.

Don't Worry...!!

decrypt.py is used to decrypt the file and recover the file contents.
python3 decrypt.py
